      },
      "text": "Visibility\n\nTOPS and YOOS everywhere: Articles, announcements, Twitter Spaces, conferences\n\n2023 Big annual meetings Open Science Themes, integrated into society comms",
      "style": {
        "font_size_pt": 11.0,
        "color": "#FFF2CC"
